Note: Tested on Mac OS X 10.6.6 with MacPorts's i386-elf compiler and mtools binaries.

Unit Tests
==========
Unit tests require CUnit to run. Get it here: <http://cunit.sourceforge.net/>
Do note that the MacPorts version of CUnit is broken as of 2011-02-14.
Run unit tests through the scons build system as follows:

    % scons check

